         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118681968">
            <form>
               <orth>lamp-eòlan</orth>
               <pron>[ɫ[ɑ̃ũ̟]</pron>
            </form>
            <def>[ɫ[ɑ̃ũ̟]mpjɔ:ɫɑ̃ṉ] Notes: oil lamp, sometimes applied to the crùisgean.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118697520">
            <form>
               <orth>lonaig</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Notes: a path through the croft.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118699032">
            <form>
               <orth>maor-cladaich</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Notes: he regulated the distribution of seaweed.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118700544">
            <form>
               <orth>milteag</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Notes: bundle of 12 “slògagan” q.v.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118702056">
            <form>
               <orth>slògag</orth>
               <pron>[sɫɔ:ɡɑɡ]</pron>
            </form>
            <def>[sɫɔ:ɡɑɡ] Notes: “slates” made up of small sheaves of corn. The seed was removed and the sheaf tied at the top of the stalks. The bottom part was then spread out like a fan. This was done in autumn. They were then laid in “bundles” of a dozen over the winter. By spring they were placed flat. Put on roof like slates.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118703784">
            <form>
               <orth>traon</orth>
               <pron>[t̪ɾw̃:ṉ]</pron>
            </form>
            <def>[t̪ɾw̃:ṉ] Notes: corncrake.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118705512">
            <form>
               <orth>beart-shùgan</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Notes: rope-making tool. <graphic url="StaffinBMacKenzieslipsillust1.jpg" width="300px"/>
            </def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118707024">
            <form>
               <orth>ceirle-shiomain</orth>
