            <def>Notes: could be a ball of hay, straw or heather rope.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118708536">
            <form>
               <orth>froigh-shnighe</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Notes: a slight dripping of water from the thatch after it had been newly thatched.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_StaffinBMacKenzieslips-idp118710048">
            <form>
               <orth>glùn</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Notes: support for the rafter between it and the top of the wall inside. <graphic url="StaffinBMacKenzieslipsillust2.jpg" width="250px"/>
            </def>
